Skillskan by Arca24 is a Skill Matching Intelligence, i.e. a semantic search engine available as a web service, which contains thousands of job descriptions and is able to read and classify documents such as CVs and job offers, to understand the meaning of the texts and rank the search results automatically. Thanks to the web server connection, it is only necessary to upload via FTP protocol the candidate’s CV you would like to analyze or the content of the job offer. The doct is inserted into the semantic engine, which springs into action, enclosing four different actions in just a few seconds:
 - data parsing and extraction;
 - data normalization;
 - semantic analysis;
 - indexing.


 Currently the semantic analysis system is available in 6 languages: Italian, English, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese.


